                    "text": "```sqf\n[player, 0.75] execVM \"setDamage.sqf\";\n```\n\nsetDamage.sqf:\n\n```sqf\n\nparams [\"_unit\", \"_damage\"];\n_unit setDamage _damage;\n\n```"
