                    "text": "```sqf\n// These all return false\n123 isEqualTypeParams [0,0,objNull,\"\"];\n[] isEqualTypeParams [0,0,objNull,\"\"];\n[1,2,player] isEqualTypeParams [0,0,objNull,\"\"];\n```"
